senses.sense_definition: A large salmonid fish, Stenodus nelma, found in Arctic freshwaters, distinguished by a large mouth with a protruding lower jaw and a high dorsal fin.

examples.text: Anglers travel to the remote northern rivers specifically to catch the elusive <w>inconnu</w>.
The <w>inconnu</w> is a predatory species that feeds on smaller fish in the cold currents.
